{"title":"Social work assessment and accreditation system: impact assessment","public_updated_at":"2016-12-20T16:42:09Z","details":{"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>An assessment of the impact a national assessment and accreditation system for child and family social workers will have on groups of people with relevant protected characteristics.</p>\n\n<p>The relevant protected characteristics, identified in the Equality Act 2010, include:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>disability</li>\n  <li>gender reassignment</li>\n  <li>pregnancy and maternity</li>\n  <li>race</li>\n  <li>religion or belief</li>\n  <li>sex and sexual orientation</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Our <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/putting-children-first-our-vision-for-childrens-social-care\">child and family social work reform plan and a report on the ‘Assessment and accreditation proof of concept’</a> are also available.</p>\n</div>","change_history":[{"public_timestamp":"2016-12-20T16:42:09.000+00:00","note":"First published."}],"documents":["<section class=\"attachment embedded\" id=\"attachment_1874084\">\n  <div class=\"attachment-thumb\">\n      <a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"thumbnail\" href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/579401/impact_assessment_child_and_family_social_work_assessment_and_accreditation.pdf\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/579401/thumbnail_impact_assessment_child_and_family_social_work_assessment_and_accreditation.pdf.png\" /></a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"attachment-details\">\n    <h2 class=\"title\"><a href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/579401/impact_assessment_child_and_family_social_work_assessment_and_accreditation.pdf\">Child and family social work assessment and accreditation: impact assessment</a></h2>\n    <p class=\"metadata\">\n        <span class=\"references\">\n          Ref: <span class=\"unique_reference\">DFE-00351-2016</span>\n        </span>\n        <span cl